casebody.data:
Johnnie L. HARRINGTON
v.
Joseph B. HALL. No. 441P92-3. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 16, 2007. Johnnie L. Harrington, Pro Se. Derrick C. Mertz, Assistant Attorney General, for State/Hall.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 15th day of October 2007 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Lee County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 16th day of October 2007."
